
" '''Sarie Marais''' " (bizwi kandi nka "My Sarie Marais",  [[Ikinyafurikansi|n'indirimbo gakondo y'Afurika y'Epfo]]<ref>https://educalingo.com/en/dic-en/sarie-marais</ref>, yakozwe bishoboka mu gihe cy'Intambara ya mbere y'Abongereza  (nko mu 1880)  Intambara ya Kabiri ya Anglo-Boer (nko mu 1900)<ref>https://www.mamalisa.com/?t=es&p=2459</ref>. Iyi ndirimbo ishobora kuba yarakuwe mu ndirimbo yaturutse mu ntambara  y'Abanyamerika yitwa "Carry me back to Tennessee" cyangwa " Sweet Ellie Rhee " hamwe n'amagambo yahinduwe muri [[Ikinyafurikansi|Afrikaans]]<ref>https://www.liquisearch.com/sarie_marais/sarie_marais_1931_-_the_first_south_african_film_with_sound</ref> .

Mu busobanuro bw'ikinyarwanda, indirimbo itangira igira iti: "Sarie Marais wanjye ari kure cyane y'umutima wanjye ariko nizeye ko tuzongera kumubona<ref>https://mubi.com/films/sarie-marais</ref>. Yatuye hafi y'uruzi rwa Mooi mbere yuko iyi ntambara itangira ... "; kandi korari ni:" Yoo, nsubiza muri Transvaal ishaje<ref>https://www.taylorfrancis.com/chapters/mono/10.4324/9780203354513-7/fictions-nation-symbol-sacrifice-1918-sarie-marais-1931-moedertjie-1931-jacqueline-maingard</ref>, aho Sarie wanjye atuye, hepfo hariya mu mirima y'ibigori hafi y'igiti cy'amahwa kibisi, ngaho abaho Sarie Marais. " "hejuru y'inyanja" (mu by'ukuri, mu 28.000 Boer abagabo batwawe nkimbohe 25 000 bajyanwa mu bwongereza<ref>https://thesamsonsedhistorian.wordpress.com/2019/12/30/my-sarie-marais/</ref><ref>https://www.researchgate.net/publication/335461461_South_African_Cinema_1</ref>

=== ''Sarie Marais'' (1931): film ya mbere yo muri Afrika yepfo ifite amajwi ===
''Sarie Marais'' kandi yari umutwe w'ishusho ya filime ya [[Afurika y’Epfo|mbere yo muri Afurika y'Epfo]] ivuga<ref>https://www.allmovie.com/movie/sarie-marais-v138696/related</ref>, iyobowe na Joseph Albrecht ( [[:af:Joseph Albrecht|af]] ) kandi yakozwe mu 1931. Ifoto yafatiwe i Johannesburg<ref>https://www.ru.ac.za/perspective/2013archive/theboersattheendoftheworld.html</ref>, ''Sarie Marais abasha'' gupakira byinshi mugihe cyiminota 10 yo kwiruka. Iyi firime yashyizwe mu nkambi ya POW yo mu [[Ubwongereza|Bwongereza]] , yibanda ku itsinda ry’imfungwa za Boer uko zigenda zireba ijisho ry’abafashwe [[Ubwongereza|n’abongereza]]<ref>https://www.jiosaavn.com/song/sarie-marais/FyE,ezpldWo</ref> . umunsi umwe imfungwa itera ijwi ryw hejuru aririmba agira ati  "My Sarie Marais". Ishyaka rye rifata izindi mfungwa, bikabaha ibyiringiro by'ejo hazaza. <ref>[http://movies2.nytimes.com/gst/movies/movie.html?v_id=138696 http://movies2.nytimes.com]</ref>

